file.name: ProgenyNode.yaml
file.content:
info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    ProgenyNode:
      type: object
      required:
      - germplasmDbId
      - progeny
      properties:
        germplasmName:
          description: A human readable name for a germplasm
          type: string
          example: A0021004
        germplasmDbId:
          description: The ID which uniquely identifies a germplasm
          type: string
          example: 01b974dc
        progeny:
          description: List of germplasm entities which are direct children of this germplasm
          items:
            required: 
            - germplasmDbId
            - parentType
            properties:
              germplasmName:
                description: The human readable name of a progeny germplasm
                type: string
                example: A0021011
              germplasmDbId:
                description: The unique identifier of a progeny germplasm
                type: string
                example: e8d5dad7
              parentType:
                description: Given a germplasm A having a progeny B and C, 'parentType' for progeny B item refers to the 'parentType' of A toward B.
                enum:
                - MALE
                - FEMALE
                - SELF
                - POPULATION
                type: string
                example: FEMALE
            type: object
          type: array
          example:
          - germplasmName: A0021011
            germplasmDbId: e8d5dad7
            parentType: FEMALE
          - germplasmName: A0021012
            germplasmDbId: ac07fbd8
            parentType: FEMALE
          - germplasmName: A0021013
            germplasmDbId: 07f45f67
            parentType: FEMALE
